Closing Statement

SLANG-Money explores a simple but fundamental idea:

Financial state can emerge from structure, without transactions, execution, or settlement.

It is released openly to encourage:

independent validation
real-world testing
safe experimentation

SLANG-Money is offered as a minimal reference implementation of that possibility
